
kubectl create deployment hello-world-app --image=registry.digitalocean.com/z9pxj2-python-example/hello-world-app:v0.1.0
kubectl scale deployment/hello-world-app --replicas=3

Check how it got divided over different nodes:
kubectl get pod -o=custom-columns=NODE:.spec.nodeName,NAME:.metadata.name --all-namespaces | grep hello-world-app


kubectl expose deployment hello-world-app --type=LoadBalancer --port=80 --target-port=80

check LB: 
doctl compute load-balancer list --format Name,Created,IP,Status

